#

Classic Borscht

75 min
$12.99
180 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEastern European

Description

A vibrant beet soup with a balance of earthy sweetness and savory depth, served hot or cold.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 2 medium, diced
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
